# slideshot Webapp — Acid Brutalist Design System

## Color Tokens

All colors MUST use Tailwind utility classes referencing CSS custom properties in `globals.css`.

### Semantic Mapping

| Purpose        | Token Class              | Hex (reference only) |
| -------------- | ------------------------ | -------------------- |
| Page bg        | `bg-background`          | #0A0A0A              |
| Card bg        | `bg-surface`             | #1A1A1A              |
| Card hover     | `bg-surface-2`           | #2A2A2A              |
| Border         | `border-border`          | #404040              |
| Primary        | `text-primary`           | #BFFF00 (acid lime)  |
| Primary fg     | `text-primary-foreground` | #0A0A0A             |
| Secondary      | `text-secondary`         | #FF2D6F (hot pink)   |
| Accent         | `text-accent`            | #7B61FF (violet)     |
| Highlight      | `text-highlight`         | #00E5FF (cyan)       |
| Text           | `text-foreground`        | #FFFFFF              |
| Text muted     | `text-muted`             | #888888              |

## Typography Hierarchy

| Element         | Classes                                                       |
| --------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Page title      | `text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-widest font-mono`      |
| Section title   | `text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-wide font-mono`         |
| Card label      | `text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-muted`      |
| Body text       | `text-sm font-mono`                                           |
| Mono / code     | `font-mono text-xs`                                           |

## Borders & Shadows

- ALL containers: `border-2 border-border`
- Rounding: `rounded-none` ONLY. NEVER `rounded`, `rounded-lg`, `rounded-xl`, `rounded-2xl`
- Hard shadow (neutral): `shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_#404040]`
- Hard shadow (primary): `shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_#BFFF00]`
- Hard shadow (hover): `shadow-[6px_6px_0px_0px_#BFFF00]`
- Press effect: `active:translate-x-1 active:translate-y-1 active:shadow-none`
- NEVER use `shadow-sm`, `shadow-md`, `shadow-lg` or blurred shadows
- NEVER use `backdrop-blur`, `backdrop-filter`, or glassmorphism

## Spacing

- `gap-4` within grids
- `p-4` / `p-5` card padding
- `px-5` / `px-6` horizontal page padding

## Animation Rules

- Hover: INSTANT color swap, NO `transition-*` on hover states
- Button press: shadow collapses, element translates via `active:` pseudo
- No bounce, no spring, no slow fade
- No `transition-colors`, `transition-all` on interactive elements

## Forbidden Patterns

- No `rounded-lg`, `rounded-xl`, `rounded-2xl`, `rounded-full` on cards/containers
- No `shadow-sm`, `shadow-md`, `shadow-lg`
- No `backdrop-blur`, `backdrop-filter`
- No gradients
- No slow transitions (`duration-200`, `duration-300`, `duration-500`)
- No `hover:brightness-*` effects

**Exceptions:**
- `rounded-full` allowed ONLY for: status indicator dots
- Arbitrary Tailwind values allowed for: hard shadow offsets
